      "title": "Covid: Five more deaths, 143 new cases added to total count",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Health Ministry says that 143 more people have tested positive for Covid-19 today, as the daily count of new cases continues to rise in the country.",
        "This brings the tally of Covid-19 cases registered in the country thus far to 665,543.",
        "Meanwhile, the Director-General of Health Services confirmed 05 new coronavirus-related deaths for July 28, pushing the country\u2019s death toll from the pandemic to 16,553."
      ],
